{"id":"harsha","term":"Harsha","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Worker or enchanter, one of the Nethinim (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezra 2:52\">Ezra 2:52</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 7:54\">Neh. 7:54</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Ezra 2:52","Nehemiah 7:54"]}